title: Still The Guy?
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and David Jacoby debate if they saw enough last night to say that James Harden can’t keep the 76ers competitive without Joel Embiid and if the Mavs can give the Suns a scare if Luka’s teammates don't produce more.
